ground-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\n     font-family:Heebo;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\n     mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">Accessibility:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Heebo;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n     color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">&nbsp;Forex signals\r\n     groups can be accessed through various platforms, including social media,\r\n     websites, or dedicated trading apps. This accessibility allows traders to\r\n     receive signals wherever they are.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\n     font-family:Heebo;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:\r\n     0pt;mso-ligatures:none\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ul><ul type=\"disc\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\n     font-family:Heebo;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\n     mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">Customization:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Heebo;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n     color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">&nbsp;Some signals groups\r\n     offer different subscription plans or signal categories tailored to\r\n     traders\' preferences, allowing for a degree of customization.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Heebo;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n     mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; backgroun